Wednesday, May 10, 1995

MERIT DOCKET

95-717. Guess v. Judges.

In Mandamus and Procedendo. On motion to dismiss, motion to dismiss by Judge Frederick Mong et al., and motion for stay of execution. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed. Motion for stay denied.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
